name: KingwoodSkins
0:
”Alexa, Ask Kingwood Skins to list the courses for this weekend”
”Alexa, Ask Kingwood Skins what course we are playing Thursday”
”Alexa, Ask Kingwood Skins what course we are playing Saturday”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kingwood skins
des: Tells you what courses the Play with the Pro and Friday through Sunday skins game will be on and at what time. You can list all the courses or ask for a particular day. You can also ask for "today" or "tomorrow". Always confirm with the clubhouse for any changes
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
